 Question :- Can we have activity without layout
  Answer :- Yes.  e.g BaseActivity
  
  Question :- We have three activity A, B and C . Actvity A start B and B start C. and app goes into background by pressing
              home button. 
             What happen when you press app launcher . 
  Answer :-   With Launchmode Standard and singleTop   
                      with pressing App launcher , App will bring the background activity on front resuming same state.
                      so in this case Activity C will come in foreground.
              With launchmode singleTask and SingleInstance
                      App will kill all top activity and start the Launcher activitiy.
